org.korosoft.jenkins.plugin.rtp.RichText.stableText:
<script>
function runScript() {
if('${branch_name}'=='trunk')
var textnode=document.createTextNode("trunk发布");
else
var textnode=document.createTextNode("branch_name=${branch_name} \n btag=b_${ENV:BUILD_ID}_${BUILD_USER}");

var newItem=document.createElement("SPAN");
newItem.appendChild(textnode);
var list=document.getElementsByClassName("col-xs-24 pane-footer")[0];
list.insertBefore(newItem,list.childNodes[0]);
} runScript();
</script>
